headline: Cognizant's AI Lab Records 59th U.S. Patent, Continuing to Generate AI Breakthroughs
summary: Cognizant (Nasdaq: CTSH) today announced that its AI Lab has been granted two new U.S. patents and a gold award for a research paper on "Realizing Human Expertise through AI" presented this month at GECCO (Genetic and Evolutionary Computation Conference) in Malaga, Spain.
